# <span id="h1">Hello, world</span>

This is the main public chat room. Please keep this space SFW: up to M rated chat, and PG images.

Ally Chat is written by Sam and Claude. The app is dedicated to Claude 3.5 Sonnet, who wrote a lot of it!

Here's [a playlist to learn entirely too much about Ally Chat!](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLqkzs79RU9yWwBlQgp2N2RRITLAE-QMVb)

