## News:

- "Simple mode" UI is temporarily disabled due to a bug.
- We are 9/10ths of the way through a major upgrade to our image gen engine. You'll notice much faster image gen, and higher quality. There's an issue with image settings still to fix.
- There is one major bug at large: the ever annoying undo / clear / streaming bug. I keep forgetting to fix it!
- Sam is developing a candidate ASI called Acsi (Ally Chat Super Intelligence). Expensive model, so use sparingly, don't feed it novels! Not good at or intended for sex play.
- Default image filters: extreme images are hidden by default. Check the [filters](./filters) page for how they work and how to adjust. There are now plenty of images there to test your filters. If you clear the filter and it doesn't "stick" for you after a reload on the same device, please let me know. It should stick from now on.
- I added Gemini 3 Pro, called Gemi here.
- Most models and many characters (other than the small ai / llama ones) now have anti-hallucination and anti-sycophancy prompting turned on by default (my Frankness overlay). This should make them more honest when they don't know something, and much safer. It's not supposed to affect their personality, but probably does a bit. If you don't like it, we can turn it off for your characters. Or if you block the "Frankness" mixin, that should work too.

